HEADWORD: Painable
<hw>Pain"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>p⟦eacute⟧nible</ets>.]</ety> <def>Causing pain; painful.</def>
